  "description": "Compute the 7th Fibonacci number",
  "source": "int main() {\n    int a = 0;\n    int b = 1;\n    int n = 7;\n    int i = 0;\n    while (i < n) {\n        int t = a + b;\n        a = b;\n        b = t;\n        i += 1;\n    }\n    return a;\n}\n",
